# PRICING VISIBILITY – STRATEGIC REDESIGN

## Atlas Health | Global Catalog Governance & Market Access Layer

### Objective

Transform Pricing Visibility from a simple configuration page into the central control tower that governs:

- Which products are visible
- Who can see them
- What prices they can see
- Which markets they can access
- Which regulations apply
- Which catalogs are synchronized to Zoho

This module should become one of the most strategic components of Atlas Health.

---

# CORE CONCEPT

Pricing Visibility should control:

1. Product Visibility
2. Price Visibility
3. Geographic Availability
4. Customer-Type Access
5. Supplier Restrictions
6. Regulatory Restrictions
7. Zoho Publishing Rules

Instead of managing visibility product-by-product, users should be able to manage visibility through dynamic rules.

